<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Swiper demo</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, minimum-scale=1, maximum-scale=1" />
    <!-- Link Swiper's CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.css">

    <!-- Demo styles -->
    <style>
        html,
        body {
            position: relative;
            height: 100%;
        }

        body {
            background: #eee;
            font-family: Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .swiper {
            width: 100%;
            padding-top: 50px;
            padding-bottom: 250px;
        }

        .reflect {
            -webkit-box-reflect: below 10px -webkit-gradient(linear, left top, left bottom, from(transparent), color-stop(50%, transparent), to(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)));
            -webkit-box-reflect: below 10px linear-gradient(transparent, transparent 50%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5));
        }

        .swiper-slide {
            background-position: center;
            background-size: cover;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.63);
        }

        .swiper-slide img {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.651);
        }

        .field-name {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 10px;
            left: 10px;
            color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.13);
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .flip-2-ver-left-2 {
            -webkit-animation: flip-2-ver-left-2 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.455, 0.030, 0.515, 0.955) both;
            animation: flip-2-ver-left-2 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.455, 0.030, 0.515, 0.955) both;
        }

        .customer-satisfaction {
        position: relative;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #a8d5e2 100%);
        padding: 40px 0;
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        animation: gradientAnimation 6s ease infinite;
    }

    .customer-satisfaction::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.322), #8BC34A, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1));
        background-size: 400% 400%;
        z-index: 1;
        animation: gradientOverlay 15s ease infinite;
    }

    .customer-satisfaction .container {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
    }

    .customer-satisfaction h2 {
        color: #00796b;
        font-family: Georgia, serif;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .customer-satisfaction p {
        color: #004d40;
        font-family: Georgia, serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    @keyframes gradientAnimation {
        0% {
            background-position: 0% 0%;
        }
        50% {
            background-position: 100% 100%;
        }
        100% {
            background-position: 0% 0%;
        }
    }

    @keyframes gradientOverlay {
        0% {
            background-position: 0% 0%;
        }
        100% {
            background-position: 100% 100%;
        }
    }

    .dark-overlay {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Adjust the opacity to control the darkness */
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .card-img-overlay {
        z-index: 2;
    }


    .swiper-slide {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .field-name {
        margin-top: 10px;
        font-size: 1.2em;
        color: #333;
        text-align: center;
        font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); /* Optional: add a slight background to improve readability */
        padding: 5px 10px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .transparent-button {
        background: transparent; /* Makes the background transparent */
        border: 2px solid #000; /* Add a border if you want */
        color: #000; /* Text color */
        padding: 10px 20px; /* Adjust padding as needed */
        font-size: 16px; /* Adjust font size */
        cursor: pointer; /* Changes cursor to pointer on hover */
        border-radius: 5px; /* Optional: Adds rounded corners */
        transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s; /* Smooth transition for hover effects */
    }

    .transparent-button:hover {
        background: #000; /* Change background color on hover */
        color: #fff; /* Change text color on hover */
    }

    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="bg"></div>
    <div class="bg bg2"></div>
    <div class="bg bg3"></div>
    <style>
        html {
            height: 100%;
        }
    
        body {
            margin: 0;
        }
    
        .bg,
        .bg2,
        .bg3 {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: -50%;
            right: -50%;
            bottom: 0;
            z-index: -1;
        }
    
        .bg {
            animation: slide 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
            background-image: linear-gradient(-60deg, #6c3 50%, #388E3C 50%);
            opacity: .5;
        }
    
        .bg2 {
            animation-direction: alternate-reverse;
            animation-duration: 4s;
        }
    
        .bg3 {
            animation-duration: 5s;
        }
    
        @keyframes slide {
            0% {
                transform: translateX(-25%);
            }
    
            100% {
                transform: translateX(25%);
            }
    
        }
    
        .white-bg-transparent {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);
            /* Adjust 0.8 to the desired opacity level */
        }
    </style>
    <%- include("partials/navbar.ejs") %>
        <br><br><br><br><br><br><br>

        <!-- Swiper -->
        <div class="swiper mySwiper" style="text-align: center; font-family: Georgia, serif;">
            <em><strong>
                    <h1>Explore Fields</h1>
                    <p>Les personnes recherchant des options au Maroc ont aussi réservé ici</p>
                </strong></em>
            <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                <% nestedArray.forEach(function(item) { %>
                    <div class="swiper-slide" style="align-items: center;">
                        <img src="<%= item[0] %>" class="reflect" width="300px" height="300px" />
                        <form action="/calendar" method="get"><button type="submit" class="transparent-button field-name" name="action" value="<%= item[1] %>">
                            <%= item[1] %>
                        </button></form>
                    </div>
                    
                <% }); %>
            </div>
            <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
        </div>
        <!-- Card Section -->
        <div class="container mt-5">
            <div style="text-align: center; font-family: Georgia, serif;">
                <em><strong>
                        <h2 class="text-center mb-4" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">Trending Destinations <img src="/images/trending-topic.png" width="30"  height="30"></h2>
                        <p style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">Ces destinations prisées ont beaucoup à offrir</p>
                    </strong></em>
            </div>
            
                <div class="row">
                    <% let usedIndices=[]; for (var j=0; j < 3; j++) { let i; do { i=Math.floor(Math.random() * nestedArray.length); }
                        while (usedIndices.includes(i)); usedIndices.push(i); %>
                        <!-- Card 1 -->
                        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                            
                                <div class="card text-bg-dark" name="action" value="<%= nestedArray[i][2] %>" >
                                    <div class="card-img-overlay dark-overlay"></div>
                                    <img src="<%= nestedArray[i][0] %>" class="card-img" height="300px" width="300px" alt="Card Image <%= j+1 %>">
                                    <div class="card-img-overlay">
                                        <h5 class="card-title">
                                            <%= nestedArray[i][1] %> <img src="/images/Flag_of_Morocco.svg.png" height="16" width="24" alt="">
                                        </h5>
                                        <p class="card-text"><small>Last updated 3 mins ago</small></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            
                        </div>
                        <% } %>
                </div>
            
        </div>

        <!-- Customer Satisfaction Section -->
        <div class="customer-satisfaction mt-5">
            <div class="container text-center">
                <h2>Customer Satisfaction</h2>
                <p>Most of our customers are absolutely thrilled with their experiences! We are dedicated to delivering
                    exceptional service and creating memorable moments for each and every guest. From the moment you
                    book with us to the end of your journey, our team is committed to ensuring your satisfaction. We
                    take great pride in the positive feedback we receive and continually strive to enhance our
                    offerings. Our goal is to exceed your expectations and make every experience unforgettable. Join the
                    many satisfied customers who have enjoyed our top-notch services and see for yourself why we are
                    highly recommended.</p>
            </div>
            <br><br>
        </div>
        <footer class="py-3 my-4">
            <ul class="nav justify-content-center border-bottom pb-3 mb-3">
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="#" class="nav-link px-2 text-body-secondary">Home</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="#" class="nav-link px-2 text-body-secondary">Features</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="#" class="nav-link px-2 text-body-secondary">Pricing</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="#" class="nav-link px-2 text-body-secondary">FAQs</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="#" class="nav-link px-2 text-body-secondary">About</a></li>
            </ul>
            <% const d=new Date(); let year=d.getFullYear(); %>
                <p>Copyright © <%= year %>
                </p>
            
        </footer>
        <!-- Swiper JS -->
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>

        <!-- Initialize Swiper -->
        <script>
            var swiper = new Swiper(".mySwiper", {
                effect: "coverflow",
                grabCursor: true,
                centeredSlides: true,
                slidesPerView: "auto",
                coverflowEffect: {
                    rotate: 15,
                    stretch: 0,
                    depth: 300,
                    modifier: 1,
                    slideShadows: true,
                },
                loop: true,
            });
        </script>
</body>
</html>